{
  "stem": "7739.3",
  "chunk_idx": 15,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "A lot of Jews came in being gassed and burned, but actually, prisoners were not-- the majority were not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "There were Russian prisoners of war, there were French, there were Yugoslavs, there were Belgians, there were-- you name it, and there they were.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "They were Germans, Austrians.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "Same thing in Buchenwald, but Buchenwald, I understand, was more prisoners of war and political prisoners.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We were just thrown in there from the other camps.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And there, since we had no work, you couldn't organize.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "You couldn't steal any food extra than what you were assigned as the-- as the rations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I remembered the-- the block [INAUDIBLE] where I was the longest time, his name was [?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Gustav. ?] He was a Russian prisoner of war.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I believe he was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "I'm not sure, but nobody knew.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And since we didn't work, except sometimes we used to volunteer to be taken down to the city of Weimar to clear the rubble so we have something to do, and we could get some extra food digging the cellars, like clearing the rubble.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So we used to volunteer, and if you were lucky enough, you spend a day or two days in the week working in Weimar.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And since we didn't work besides this, I figured there's so many people being brought in from different camps, why don't I look around in the other barracks?",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe I'll find my father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Maybe I'll find my brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "On this point, we'll stop for a moment.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
